                  <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                  Decorative designs:
                  <locus target="#iir(ecto) #1r #29r #57v #81r #92r #100r #103v #110v #119r #137v #139r #143v #144v" facs="002 004 032 061 084 095 103 107 114 122 141 142 147 148">fols. iir(ecto), 1r, 29r, 57v, 81r, 92r, 100r, 103v, 110v, 119r, 137v, 139r, 143v, 144v</locus> (ḫarägs in black ink);
